<div class="bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
    <nav class="flex items-center text-sm font-medium mb-6">
      <a href="<%= root_path %>" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">Home</a>
      <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-300 mx-1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M5.555 17.776l8-16 .894.448-8 16-.894-.448z" />
      </svg>
      <a href="<%= products_path %>" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">Products</a>
      <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-300 mx-1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M5.555 17.776l8-16 .894.448-8 16-.894-.448z" />
      </svg>
      <span class="text-gray-900">New Product</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- Page header -->
    <div class="md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between mb-8">
      <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl sm:truncate">
          Add New Product
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-gray-500">Create a new product listing for your store.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Product form -->
    <%= render 'form', product: @product %>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Tips sidebar -->
<div class="fixed inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none z-10" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="hidden lg:block absolute right-0 top-32 w-80 px-6 py-8 bg-yellow-50 rounded-l-lg shadow-lg pointer-events-auto">
    <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-yellow-800 mb-3">Tips for Great Products</h4>
    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-yellow-700">
      <li class="flex">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <span>Use descriptive, keyword-rich titles to help customers find your product.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <span>Upload high-quality images (at least 1000x1000px) to showcase your product.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <span>Provide detailed specifications and measurements to reduce customer questions.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <span>Set competitive prices by researching similar products on the platform.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <span>Be accurate about shipping times and inventory to maintain customer trust.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="mt-6 text-sm">
      <a href="#" class="text-yellow-800 font-medium hover:text-yellow-900">Seller guidelines →</a>
    </div>
    <button type="button" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-500" aria-label="Close tips">
      <svg class="h-5 w-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>
</div>